2.Design a web page that includes an image, hyperlink, and a nested table.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Web Page with Image, Link, and Nested Table</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>My Sample Web Page</h1>
<!-- Image -->
<h2>My Image</h2>
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Sample Image">
<!-- Hyperlink -->
<h2>Visit a Website</h2>
<p>
Click here to visit 
<a href="https://www.google.com" target="_blank">Google</a>
</p>
<!-- Nested Table -->
<h2>Student Details</h2>
<table border="1" cellpadding="10">
<tr>
<th>Name</th>
<th>Subjects & Marks</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>John Doe</td>
<td>
<!-- Nested Table -->
<table border="1" cellpadding="5">
<tr>
<th>Subject</th>
<th>Marks</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Mathematics</td>
<td>85</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Computer Science</td>
<td>92</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Physics</td>
<td>78</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
